message: Hi Bob, I'm offering this product to you for $110. I believe it will be very valuable for you.

Hi Alice, thank you for your offer. However, I believe $110 is a bit high. Given the market conditions, I can offer $90 for the product. This would still give you a good profit margin while being a fair price for me.
Hi Bob, I appreciate your offer. However, the value of this product is considerably higher than what you're offering. I'm willing to come down to $100, which I believe is a fair compromise.
